                        "revenge an insult"
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "sense_id": "08d33abb-6119-30a5-bf7e-d4e41e87b42a",
                    "sense_definition": "To take action to hurt someone who has hurt you, usually used reflexively.",
                    "learner_level": "C2",
                    "frequency": "VeryLow",
                    "semantic_group_id": "action_reflexive",
                    "name_type": "no",
                    "examples": [
                        {
                            "text": "She sought to <w>revenge</w> herself on her ex-husband for his lies."
                        },
                        {
                            "text": "The hero planned to <w>revenge</w> himself upon the villains who stole his land."
